title: Evanescence Other Collections
description:
This is a compilation torrent of Evanescence collections that I have, it contains:

1. Official Acoustics, Acapellas and Instrumentals

2. Movie Soundtracks

    - 2011 - Muppets - The Green Album
    - 2012 - Avengers Assemble Soundtrack
    - 2012 - Underworld Awakening Soundtrack

3. Collaborations
     - [2003] Big Dismisal - Believe
     - [2004] Broken
     - [2007] Finger Eleven
     - [2007] Korn - MTV Unplugged
     - [2007] My Coke Fest
     - [2012] Lzzy Hale
     - [2012] Restore Freedom Gala
     - [2013] Wellspring (Paula Cole)
     - [2014] Bluegrass Underground
     - David Hodges

4. Covers

     - Another One Bites the Dust (Queen Snippet)
     - Baby Got Back (Snippet)
     - Blind (Korn Snippet)
     - Caught A Little Baby Bumble-Bee
     - (Don't Fear) The Reaper (Blue Oyster Cult)

If you have something I don't please give a download link in the comment section or if you have a better quality of something. Just sharing what I have with other fans.
